rest_of_day_open:

critical_positive:

I was able to express myself well so some extend and he seemed to not have any problems talkign about his own opinions and experiences.
critical_negative:

I think he was pretty bored by me or the conversation at times, can't really blame him though, I am just a random stranger.

rest_of_day_open: I believe that my rest of the week will be similar to the previous weeks: Calm, uninteresting, and happy. I want to hang out with a friend so hopefully this week will be different. critical_positive: The fact that we both wanted to talk about the issues regarding COVID-19 helped us to start a conversation. We had similar feelings regarding the issues that this pandemic has brought. We also had similar opinions regarding controversial topics in the US. We both were respectful and friendly which really helped the conversation to bloom
critical_negative: Probably the only thing that could have interfered is that we both had strong accents. That may could have interfered when sharing a message.
